    ðŸ”¹ `--device DEVICE` --> ðŸ’¾ Specifies the device or image file to test (e.g., `/dev/sda1` or `disk.img`).
    ðŸ”¹ `--format FORMAT` --> ðŸ—‚ Specifies the file system format (e.g., `ext2`, `ext4`, `fat`). If not specified, `grub-fstest` will attempt to detect the format automatically.

